node.text:
Watch @dcappellamusic’s Orlando and Joe as they give an extended look at the 2021 Disney Rainbow Collection. 

In celebration of Pride Month, The Walt Disney Company is giving funds as part of our ongoing commitment to organizations around the world that support LGBTQ+ communities. Learn more at RainbowDisneyCollection.com.
